Description:
    Generates the appropriate XML structure file and/or database migration(s) for Esagon bindings

Example (XML sctructure file generation):
    rails generate acts_as_esagon --xml

    This will create:
        tmp/esagon.xml

Example (database migration):
    rails generate acts_as_esagon [Model] --migration

    This will create:
        db/migrate/yyyyMMddssssss_add_esagon_bindings_to_<model>.rb
